Hello,

At the moment, it is not possible to download all profile pictures uploaded by user in Confluence. 

The workaround available is to use the URL such as followings:
{code}
http://server_base_url/download/attachments/pageid/attachment_filename
{code}
where additional properties such as {{pageid}} and {{attachment_filename}} can be obtained from Confluence database using the foolowing query:
{code:sql}
SELECT a.pageid, a.title FROM attachments a JOIN os_propertyentry op ON a.title = op.string_val;
{code}

Please assess the possibility of having this feature available on the future version of Confluence.

Thank you and regards,
Lazuardi

